    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>If you want to convert list into the CSV format .........</strong> </p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; ids = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\nids.add(\"1\");\nids.add(\"2\");\nids.add(\"3\");\nids.add(\"4\");\n\n// CSV format\nString csv = ids.toString().replace(\"[\", \"\").replace(\"]\", \"\")\n            .replace(\", \", \",\");\n\n// CSV format surrounded by single quote \n// Useful for SQL IN QUERY\n\nString csvWithQuote = ids.toString().replace(\"[\", \"'\").replace(\"]\", \"'\")\n            .replace(\", \", \"','\");\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
