    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here is code given below to convert a List into a comma separated string without iterating List explicitly for that you have to make a list and add item in it than convert it into a comma separated string</p>\n\n<p>Output of this code will be: Veeru,Nikhil,Ashish,Paritosh </p>\n\n<p>instead of output of list [Veeru,Nikhil,Ashish,Paritosh]</p>\n\n<pre><code>String List_name;\nList&lt;String&gt; myNameList = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\nmyNameList.add(\"Veeru\");\nmyNameList.add(\"Nikhil\");\nmyNameList.add(\"Ashish\");\nmyNameList.add(\"Paritosh\");\n\nList_name = myNameList.toString().replace(\"[\", \"\")\n                    .replace(\"]\", \"\").replace(\", \", \",\");\n</code></pre>\n"
