    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use below code if object has attibutes under it.</p>\n\n<pre><code>String getCommonSeperatedString(List&lt;ActionObject&gt; actionObjects) {\n    StringBuffer sb = new StringBuffer();\n    for (ActionObject actionObject : actionObjects){\n        sb.append(actionObject.Id).append(\",\");\n    }\n    sb.deleteCharAt(sb.lastIndexOf(\",\"));\n    return sb.toString();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
